h. It's the schemers that put you where you are. You were a schemer, you had plans, and, uh, look where that got you.<br />\n<br />\nI just did what I do best. I took your little plan, and I turned it on itself. Look what I did to this city with a few drums of gas and a couple of bullets, hmm? You know what I noticed? Nobody panics when things go according to plan. Even when the plan is horrifying. If tomorrow I told the press that, like, a gang-banger would get shot, or a truckload of soldiers will be blown up, nobody panics. Because it's all part of the plan. But when I say that one little old mayor will die, well then everybody loses their minds!"},{"pid":"12b7bba2f569c35735264551b79b7d91e6aadd7b","tid":1338291,"uid":13946,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見set今次終點喺修頓嗰位飲緊大支裝檸樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230e3483019ac7a358ad54bb0050492a74fb005c","tid":1338291,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}